briefdescription.para: CFS Telemetry Output Task (TO) application entry point.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: CFS Telemetry Output Task application entry point. This function performs app initialization, then waits for the cFE ES Startup Sync, then executes the RPR main processing loop.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: If there is an unrecoverable failure during initialization the main loop is never executed and the application will exit.
